1. Go to https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/installer/ and download the installer
2. install it onto your computer
3. open up mysql workbench and login (during set up you will need to create a username and password
   - this is where you use it)
4. You should see around the bottom left hand corner a thing called schemas. click on it.
5. Near the word Query you will see what looks like 2 hockey pucks stacked on each other click it and call it database
   then hit apply.
6. You will see data base on the left side now. Double click on it so it turns bold
7. Click it again and now beside the hockey pucks you should see a table creator click it.
8. In the resources tab you should see table-how-to. Make your table exactly like the image.
9. Hit apply - done.